4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior knowledge. This 16-week program provides live online classes, typically three times a week, for up to 16 students. The curriculum covers essential skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, along with cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence. Students learn about data loss prevention strategies and compliance with international standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Upon completion, participants receive an official certificate recognized by multiple institutions. Classes are available in English and Spanish. For more details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop